{"tid":1594383,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚好撚傷心，文記車仔麵已經變晒","createTime":"2019-09-25T14:04:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T06:07:33.000Z","uid":8687,"like":7,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"fab98dfe44bb48fe0535ee2f20a36268c4b89842","tid":1594383,"uid":8687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:04:39.000Z","msg":"柚皮切到蘿蔔咁厚咁大舊，有渣<br />\n玻璃魷魚唔玻璃<br />\n五花腩又係厚切有渣<br />\n豬油渣手指咁大又粗<br />\n最緊要上枱係唔柒熱既<br />\n係得隻蛋入得下口<br />\n當初你一間開三間 D 料 D 味都仲 keep 到<br />\n唔知係咪 D 材料上次比 TG 攪到要換過晒定點<br />\n但冇理由唔入返舊貨<br />\n係呀，好柒飽呀，因為樣樣料個 size 大左一倍丫嘛，但係你老味咁大件點入味呀<br />\n以後深水埗又 blacklist 多間<br />\n好失望"},{"pid":"e91523ddf6d00469d09da9965264dca63ef46b67","tid":1594383,"uid":8687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:04:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf4823a7f1be9a20f1f3604b3e7e68f61f6a45f8","tid":1594383,"uid":263618,"like":50,"dislike":6,"score":44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:05:27.000Z","msg":"藍絲舖頭，不了"},{"pid":"8949b2fa3204d904aa5b5ebd2c95a83a260f4fb3","tid":1594383,"uid":8687,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"cf4823a7f1be9a20f1f3604b3e7e68f61f6a45f8","tid":1594383,"uid":263618,"like":50,"dislike":6,"score":44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:05:27.000Z","msg":"藍絲舖頭，不了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:06:26.000Z","msg":"唔係話比人屈咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01cccdca875405c7882af9e037c42ee88f0404ca","tid":1594383,"uid":38904,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:06:42.000Z","msg":"藍屎舖頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話知佢請我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2bdda062a9b7c20fe1c2241f7c2d66879b2675","tid":1594383,"uid":263618,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4